name: Oliver Randall
profile_summary: The user is a 28-year-old man who goes by "He/Him/His" and hails from Seattle, Washington but currently living in Los Angeles, California. He is a 6'1 tall, straight, White Caucasian with Virgo as his zodiac sign and an INTJ personality type considered to be an "architect" or "strategist". He graduated from the University of California and works in the tech industry as a Software Engineer. Despite being Agnostic and politically liberal, his core values are hard work, creativity, adventure, fitness, and family. He enjoys several hobbies: hiking, gaming, cooking, reading, and technology. Spanish and English are the two languages he speaks fluently. He has a cat, avoids smoking, drugs and marijuana, but drinks occasionally. While he doesn't have children, he hopes to in the future. His relationship intentions are long-term and monogamous.
